===Etymology===

A translation of the English "muskrat."  From [[사향]] (''sahyang'', "musk") + [[쥐]] (''jwi'', "rat")

===Noun===

'''사향쥐''' (sa.hyang.jwi)

# A [[muskrat]], ''[[Ondatra zibethicus]]''.

